CSRP V1 RELEASE

LAW ENFORCEMENT REVAMP
Our excellent law enforcement departments have recieved a much-needed re-haul. With new vehicle models, new livery designs, and new uniforms, our departments in CSRP are some of the best that FiveM offers. There is no better time to join a LEO department!

PIGGY BACK
Now, you can piggyback with a friend! Type /piggyback in chat near another player, and you can run around while riding the back of another player!

GUN STORE REVAMP
Our gun stores have been a staple in reducing RDM and making the weapon experience realistic. Now, all gun stores feature a custom interior, and weapons will now appear on the counter instead of the wall!

